      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box aw-briefly\">\n\t\t\t各位关注中国和外国外交新闻的<br/>\n请不要看中文媒体发布的通稿。那是严重扭曲的文宣作品，你会觉得全世界领导人访华都是来聆听包子圣训的。如果你以中文媒体的报道为准，你已经进了包子的精神猪圈了。<br/>\n<br/>\n比如这次布林肯访华，请移步美国国务院网站看布林肯记者招待会全文<br/>\n请看下面两段<br/>\nWe are for de-risking and diversifying.  That means investing in our own capacities and in secure, resilient supply chains; pushing for level playing fields for our workers and our companies; defending against harmful trade practice; and protecting our critical technologies so that they aren’t used against us.  I made clear that we’ll continue to take targeted actions that are necessary to protect U.S. national security.<br/>\n<br/>\nIn my meetings, I also discussed human rights.  The United States and the international community remain deeply concerned about PRC human rights violations, including in Xinjiang, in Tibet, and Hong Kong.  I also specifically raised wrongfully detained U.S. citizens and those facing exit bans.  There is no higher priority for me than the safety and well-being of U.S. citizens overseas, and I’ll continue to work intensively to secure their release and their safe return home.<br/>\n<br/>\n这不是对着王毅和包子说：脱钩（美其名曰去风险化）不可避免，你们人权糟糕么？<br/>\n<br/>\n再说一遍<br/>\n美国不是中国人的民主大救星，无论哪任总统，第一位的利益是美国人的利益。中国人自己支持包子独裁，美国人也没有办法。美国人支持香港、新疆、西藏，是因为这些地区的人民用自己的鲜血做出了抵抗。<br/>\n第二，布林肯访华，虽然是五年来第一次，但是不要把它看成是标志性作秀。布林肯访华非常务实，目的就是保持中美对话。就是这样，中国还是拒绝恢复军事上的通讯，是非常幼稚的无赖行为。美国就像一个成年人，面对一个满地打滚的无赖小孩，难道成年人也躺下一起打滚？\t\t<div class=\"aw-stretch-content-button-container\"><button class=\"aw-stretch-content-button\" type=\"button\"></button></div></div>",
